quote><blockquote>我也是, 不過這不好</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你需要交際應酬時會感到很不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而會覺得去唔去都冇所謂，反正都係應酬，有少少嫌麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabbd9bf7e7c6c299535e6126d5a6cb08e9f715d","tid":195274,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太毒人生好無聊</blockquote><br />\n自問我既人生真係好撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又冇咩&quot;試&quot;好"},{"pid":"2fff1fc3bde08b8f9a338304921e5cc9deb21bc8","tid":195274,"uid":34642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"好正常"},{"pid":"994c1ea743976bb54a3525995b7455dba492c963","tid":195274,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太毒人生好無聊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至少感到舒適"},{"pid":"a6941fea9896ba9f1c8b75a82d94957f954ae141","tid":195274,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我也是, 不過這不好</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你需要交際應酬時會感到很不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而會覺得去唔去都冇所謂，反正都係應酬，有少少嫌麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我也以為是這樣, 但是事與願違, 總有一些是不能避免的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm